  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of libsigc++</title>

    <para>
      First, fix detecting Boost when configuring this package:
    </para>

<screen><userinput remap="pre">sed -i "s/'system',//" meson.build</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install <application>libsigc++</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir bld &amp;&amp;
cd    bld &amp;&amp;

meson setup --prefix=/usr --buildtype=release .. &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the results, issue: <command>ninja test</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

